cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"q4fH06mIjuK3"},"source":["#### Activity 1: Print name and email id\n","\n","Here you need to accept the name and email id from the user and display it.\n","\n","For example: \n","\n","             Enter your name : Sam\n","             Enter your email id : sam@gmail.com\n","             Hello Sam, your email id is sam@gmail.com\n","\n","Follow the steps given below to achieve the desired result:\n","\n","  - **Step 1:** Ask the user to enter a name using `input()` function and store it in the `name` variable.\n","  - **Step 2:** Ask the user to enter an email id using `input()` function and store it in the `email` variable.\n","  - **Step 3:** Print the values of `name` and `email` variables using `print()` function.\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"id":"4EAoTskqg041","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1621461896152,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":12353,"user":{"displayName":"Isabella Schoffler","photoUrl":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GhLOIF36CttK97G8Q1cIOIFUaFGwg0Je1g5W1YY=s64","userId":"16198738062751160932"}},"outputId":"74640c5c-96b7-415e-d0d3-d8c16ad262d6"},"source":["# Write your code here\n","# Step 1: Ask the user to enter a name\n","name=input(\"Enter your name.\")\n","\n","# Step 2: Ask the user to enter an email id\n","email=input(\"Enter your email adress please.\")\n","\n","# Step 3: Print name and email id\n","print(\"Hello\",name,\"your email adress is\",email)"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","text":["Enter your name.Imid\n","Enter your email adress please.LNKU\n","Hello Imid your email adress is LNKU\n"],"name":"stdout"}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"xJlPs9X9oeRw"},"source":["---"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"qA-b1CdeofKc"},"source":["#### Activity 2: Display the average of marks in 3 subjects\n","\n","Calculate the average of marks scored in 3 subjects and display the result.\n","\n","For example: \n","\n","    mark1= 56\n","    mark2= 73\n","    mark3= 69\n","    Average Marks = 66\n","\n","Follow the steps given below to achieve the desired result:\n","\n","- **Step 1:** Declare three variables `mark1`, `mark2` and `mark3` respectively and store any numerical values in it.\n","\n","- **Step 2:** Use another variable `sum` to store the sum of values in  `mark1`, `mark2` and `mark3` variables.\n","\n","- **Step 3:** Calculate the average by dividing the `sum` variable by 3. Store the result in the variable `average`.\n","\n","- **Step 4:** Print the average marks."]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"id":"AtvPTG3kpBoS","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1621462027128,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":796,"user":{"displayName":"Isabella Schoffler","photoUrl":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GhLOIF36CttK97G8Q1cIOIFUaFGwg0Je1g5W1YY=s64","userId":"16198738062751160932"}},"outputId":"68e2de6f-a3f3-4bf2-f7e8-e31bb2600d90"},"source":["# Write your code here\n","# Step 1: Declare three variables 'mark1', 'mark2' and 'mark3' respectively and store any numerical values in them\n","mark1=56\n","mark2=73\n","mark3=69\n","# Step 2: Use 'sum' variable to store their sum\n","sum=mark1+mark2+mark3\n","# Step 3: Calculate the average by dividing the 'sum' by 3 and storing it in the variable 'average' \n","average=sum/3\n","\n","# Step 4: Use print() function to display the average marks\n","print(\"The average of all the marks are\",average)"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","text":["The average of all the marks are 66.0\n"],"name":"stdout"}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"KOVBiUSMzut1"},"source":["---"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"BNlGj8NNJ1Y0"},"source":["### Submitting the Project:\n","\n","1. After finishing the project, click on the **Share** button on the top right corner of the notebook. A new dialog box will appear.\n","\n","  <img src='https://student-